This is the first post on this site. It's built with [Astro](https://astro.build)
for the static site generation and [Keystatic](https://keystatic.com) for
content editing.

Edit or delete this post from the Keystatic Admin UI at `/keystatic`, or by
editing this file directly at `src/content/blog/hello-world.mdoc`.
